<td style="padding:0;vertical-align:inherit;height:22px">1</td>
</tr>
<tr style="vertical-align:middle">
<td style="vertical-align:inherit;padding:0"></td>
<td style="padding:0;vartical-align:inherit;height:18px;width:22px">a</td>
<td style="padding:0;vartical-align:inherit;height:18px;width:22px">b</td>
<td style="padding:0;vartical-align:inherit;height:18px;width:22px">c</td>
<td style="padding:0;vartical-align:inherit;height:18px;width:22px">d</td>
<td style="padding:0;vartical-align:inherit;height:18px;width:22px">e</td>
<td style="padding:0;vartical-align:inherit;height:18px;width:22px">f</td>
<td style="padding:0;vartical-align:inherit;height:18px;width:22px">g</td>
<td style="padding:0;vartical-align:inherit;height:18px;width:22px">h</td>
<td style="vertical-align:inherit;padding:0"></td>
</tr>
</table>
<div class="thumbcaption">Black to play draws (<a href="#CITEREFMullerLamprecht2001">Muller &amp; Lamprecht 2001</a>:23).</div>
</div>
</div>
<p>In an endgame, two <dfn id=""><a href="/wiki/Glossary_of_chess#minor_piece" title="Glossary of chess"><span title="See entry at: Glossary of chess § minor piece" style="color:inherit;" class="glossary-link">minor pieces</span></a></dfn> are approximately equivalent to a rook plus one pawn. The <a href="/wiki/Pawn_structure" title="Pawn structure">pawn structure</a> is important. The two pieces have the advantage if the opponent's pawns are weak. <a href="/wiki/Initiative_(chess)" title="Initiative (chess)">Initiative</a> is more important in this endgame than any other. The general outcome can be broken down by the number of pawns.</p>
<ul>
<li>The two pieces have one or more extra pawns: always a win for the pieces.</li>
<li>Same number of pawns: usually a draw but the two pieces win more often than the rook.</li>
<li>The rook has one extra pawn: usually a draw but either side may have winning chances, depending on positional factors.</li>
<li>The rook has two additional pawns: normally a win for the rook (<a href="#CITEREFFineBenko2003">Fine &amp; Benko 2003</a>:449–58).</li>
</ul>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Queen_versus_two_rooks">Queen versus two rooks</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Chess_endgame&amp;action=edit&amp;section=23" title="Edit section: Queen versus two rooks">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
